name: Yanxi Palace: Princess Adventures
overview: A determined Qing dynasty princess contends with palace intrigue and a vendetta against her family while navigating the treacherous terrain of romance.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Rejected by Mongolian Prince Lhawang Dorji, Princess Zhaohua sets out to make him fall in love with her. Imperial guard Fuk'anggan plots revenge.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Fuk'anggan becomes Zhaohua's confidant and conspires with Princess Siwan, who schemes to earn Lhawang Dorji's goodwill.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Princess Siwan sets a deadly trap for Zhaohua, who accepts punishment for a crime she did not commit. Wei Yingluo pays Princess Siwan a visit.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: Wei Yingluo warns Zhaohua about Fuk'anggan's baffling romantic gesture. Fuk'anggan reveals to Zhaohua his vendetta against Wei Yingluo.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Wei Yingluo makes a shocking revelation about Fuk'anggan's family. Zhaohua's whereabouts remain unknown, and a dark presence haunts the palace.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Fuk'anggan's and Princess Siwan's lives hang by a thread as Zhaohua confronts a demon within -- but nothing is what it seems.
